The paper deals with image retrieval and metric learning, which are both topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves learning shared visual characteristics across object classes, which is a task that involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using a separate encoder to learn these characteristics, which is a technique commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
